     FALDPL38 IF  E           K        DISK
     FADAPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FANZPP11 O   E           K        DISK                      A
      *---------------------------------------------------
     E                    ERR     1  20 60
     E                    PG        999  1
      *---------------------------------------------------
     I@INFDS      DS
     I                                     *STATUS  @STTS
     I                                    B 370 3710@@LIN
     I                                    B 378 3790@@REC
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      * SYSTEM TIME(6) + DATE(8)
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WWTIME
     I                                        1   60WTIME
     I                                        1   40WTIM4
     I                                        1   20WTIMH
     I                                        3   40WTIMM
